'''尼可拉斯·彼得·森澤爾'''（{{lang-en|Nicholas Peter Senzel}}，{{bd|1995年|6月29日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於辛辛那提紅人。他在2016年大聯盟選秀中於第一輪第2順位被紅人隊選走，並在2019年登上大聯盟。
==職業生涯==
===辛辛那提紅人===
森澤爾在2019年5月3日登上大聯盟，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.redreporter.com/2019/5/3/18528214/nick-senzel-to-make-major-league-debut|title=Nick Senzel To Make Major League Debut|author=Aaron Michael|website=Red Reporter|publisher=SB Nation|date=May 3, 2019|access-date=May 3, 2019|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503225535/https://www.redreporter.com/2019/5/3/18528214/nick-senzel-to-make-major-league-debut|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cincinnati.com/story/sports/mlb/reds/2019/05/03/cincinnati-reds-called-up-nick-senzel-because-they-need-him/1094793001/ |title=Cincinnati Reds called up Nick Senzel because they need him |author=John Fay |date=May 3, 2019 |publisher=USA Today |work=www.cincinnati.com |access-date=May 4, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225055525/https://www.cincinnati.com/story/sports/mlb/reds/2019/05/03/cincinnati-reds-called-up-nick-senzel-because-they-need-him/1094793001/ }}</ref>他在初登板的第5個打席敲出內野安打，成為他的大聯盟首安。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/giants-spoil-nick-senzels-debut-with-epic-eight-run-comeback-against-reds/ |title=Giants spoil Nick Senzel's debut with epic eight-run comeback against Reds |author=Mike Axisa |date=May 3, 2019 |publisher=CBS Sports Interactive |work=www.cbssports.com |access-date=May 4, 2019 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607160150/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/giants-spoil-nick-senzels-debut-with-epic-eight-run-comeback-against-reds/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-makes-mlb-debut |title=Nick Senzel makes MLB debut |author=Mark Sheldon |date=May 4, 2019 |publisher=Major League Baseball |work=www.mlb.com |access-date=May 4, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024207/https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-makes-mlb-debut |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月4日，他敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2019/05/04/pillar-robs-one-homer-reds-blast-five-others-giants-crushed-in-cincinnati/ |title=Pillar robs one homer, Reds blast five others, Giants crushed in Cincinnati |author=Kerry Crowley |date=May 4, 2019 |publisher=MediaNews Group, Inc. |work=www.mercurynews.com |access-date=May 6, 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506235939/https://www.mercurynews.com/2019/05/04/pillar-robs-one-homer-reds-blast-five-others-giants-crushed-in-cincinnati/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>整個5月份他的打擊率為2成79，並敲出4轟與12分打點。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/nationals/bees-circle-senzel-homers-twice-as-reds-swarm-giants-12-4/2019/05/06/bb8b3fe8-703a-11e9-9331-30bc5836f48e_story.html?noredirect=on |title=Bees circle, Senzel homers twice as Reds swarm Giants 12-4 |author=Joey Kay |date=May 6, 2019 |publisher=WP Company LLC |work=www.washingtonpost.com |access-date=May 13, 2019 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>

9月12日，他因為盂唇撕裂傷而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cincinnati.com/story/sports/mlb/reds/2019/09/12/nick-senzel-injury-rookie-outfielder-out-year-torn-labrum/2307401001/ |title=Cincinnati Reds rookie Nick Senzel out for season with a torn labrum, may need surgery |author=Bob Nightengale |date=September 12, 2019 |work=wwww.cincinnati.com |access-date=January 2, 2020 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914094401/https://www.cincinnati.com/story/sports/mlb/reds/2019/09/12/nick-senzel-injury-rookie-outfielder-out-year-torn-labrum/2307401001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>整季他的打擊率為2成56，並敲出12轟與42分打點。

2020年8月至9月間，他因為不明原因缺席27場比賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-goes-on-il-mike-moustakas-returns|title=Senzel lands on IL, but Reds get Moose back|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=August 19, 2020|access-date=January 5, 2021|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309195946/https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-goes-on-il-mike-moustakas-returns|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-activated-from-injured-list|title=Senzel comes off IL for Reds' doubleheader|website=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|date=September 14, 2020|access-date=January 5, 2021|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108153119/https://www.mlb.com/news/nick-senzel-activated-from-injured-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年他的打擊率僅1成86，並敲出2轟與8分打點。2021年6月13日，森澤爾因為膝蓋發炎進入60天傷兵名單。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/06/reds-reinstate-aristides-aquino-from-injured-list.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2021-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211103181743/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/06/reds-reinstate-aristides-aquino-from-injured-list.html }}</ref>
